{"tid":1496060,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"823人鏈 唔想掂到人隻手嘅全部同我入嚟","createTime":"2019-08-22T10:39:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T16:34:33.000Z","uid":173106,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4e34af1cfe5b58624cd5f07300c6168a6f287f04","tid":1496060,"uid":173106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T10:39:03.000Z","msg":"無論你係有手汗定有潔癖<br />\n總之唔想掂到人隻手或者唔想人地掂到你嘅 <br />\n都整張banner<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大細你自己話事 好似個示意圖咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5271uMa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5271uMa.jpg&h=b747879b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n見到有人話用雨傘或者戴手套 <br />\n唔係話唔得<br />\n但反正呢個活動都係做俾人睇<br />\n咁不如做盡佢 做得好好睇睇 <br />\n記者或者航拍影出嚟都靚啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBanner個內容就你自己喜歡啦<br />\n或者參考吓呢個post去整啦<br />\n將人鏈戰術升級! 向全世界講多謝!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1495307\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1495307</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"01075a33419412d864c62a61bfe003561fedb4ed","tid":1496060,"uid":173106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T10:40:53.000Z","msg":"聽日見！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FefVzgz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFefVzgz.jpg&h=4c84cb39&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"42819cb82989a2f8e2773a76d97485772f1811f4","tid":1496060,"uid":203417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T10:40:53.000Z","msg":"幾好，不過睇落個場唔咁逼，又俾位啲三毛藍屍入"},{"pid":"58091994ceef29003ba1219d88e17b9ede933cf9","tid":1496060,"uid":173106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T10:41:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HDaa7BM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHDaa7BM.jpg&h=b014aa41&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6072724ebfcd2fb8507187c42690f07ab2ae5ef2","tid":1496060,"uid":173106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"